OL,3,GNEWSCNew masthead design for Radio
OL,4,CTimes from tomorrow
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe new edition of the Radio Times `
OL,7,Fout tomorrow ` will see the
OL,8,Fintroduction of a new logo/masthead.
OL,10,FThe updated lettering is a nod to the
OL,11,Flogo used in the 1970s, 1980s and
OL,12,F1990s.
OL,14,FThis is the first significant visual
OL,15,Fidentity refresh for the Radio Times
OL,16,Fbrand in more than 20 years, developed
OL,17,Fwith branding agency Why Projects.
OL,19,FThe update includes a custom logotype
OL,20,Fand icon by type designer Rob Clarke,
OL,21,Fpaired with the contemporary Degular
OL,22,Ftypeface.
OL,23,EPub: 02-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
