OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCNew masthead design for Radio
OL,4,CTimes from tomorrow
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe rebrand addresses a longstanding
OL,7,Fissue: the 103-year-old publication had
OL,8,Foperated as multiple disconnected
OL,9,Fproducts rather than a unified brand,
OL,10,Fwith separate identities across its
OL,11,Fmagazine, website and digital platforms
OL,12,Fthat lacked cohesion.
OL,14,FRather than abandoning its heritage,
OL,15,Fthe team drew inspiration from Radio
OL,16,FTimes' peak circulation era in the
OL,17,F1970s and 80s, reinterpreting those
OL,18,Felements for contemporary use.
OL,23,EPub: 02-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15803
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1776366672
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCNew masthead design for Radio
OL,4,CTimes from tomorrow
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe rebrand extends beyond visuals to
OL,7,Finclude motion design, sonic branding
OL,8,Fand unified tone of voice across all
OL,9,Fplatforms.
OL,11,FSenior design Nick Wells says the goal
OL,12,Fis repositioning Radio Times as part of
OL,13,Fthe entertainment industry rather than
OL,14,Fjust publishing, helping audiences
OL,15,Fnavigate content "with confidence,
OL,16,Fpersonality and fun."
